Package: keycloak-ssh-auth
Version: 0.5.0
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6, libpam0g (>= 1.5.3), openssh-server
Pre-Depends: dpkg (>= 1.22)
Maintainer: Norbert Krucky <norbert.krucky@pm.me>
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://git.server.nk-it.cloud/nk-dev/keycloak-ssh-auth
Description: Keycloak SSH Authentication via Device Authorization Grant
 Provides PAM-based SSH authentication using Keycloak SSO.
 Uses RFC 8628 Device Authorization Grant for headless and
 desktop SSH sessions. Zero-config for NKIT infrastructure.
